\c 44
\s Ukukhululwa kwasendulo lokuhlupheka kwalesisikhathi
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela, esamadodana kaKora, Masikili
\p
\v 1 Nkulunkulu, sizwile ngendlebe zethu, obaba basitshelile\x + Hlu. 6.13. Hlab. 78.3. Eks. 12.26.\x*, umsebenzi owawenza ensukwini zabo, ensukwini zendulo\x + Isa. 23.7. Hlab. 77.5.\x*.
\v 2 Wena ngesandla sakho wazixotsha izizwe elifeni\x + Josh. 3.10. 2 Lan. 20.7. Dute. 7.1. Hlu. 6.9. Neh. 9.24. Hlab. 78.55. 80.8. Seb. 7.45. 13.19.\x*, wabahlanyela bona\x + Eks. 15.17. Hlab. 80.8.\x*; wazihlupha izizwe, kodwa wabasabalalisa bona\x + Gen. 43.14.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba kabadlanga ilifa lelizwe ngenkemba yabo, lengalo yabo kayibasindisanga\x + Josh. 24.12.\x*, kodwa isandla sakho sokunene, lengalo yakho, lokukhanya kobuso bakho\x + Hlab. 89.15.\x*, ngoba wawubathanda\x + Dute. 4.37. 7.7,8. 10.15.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Wena uyiNkosi yami, Nkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 74.12.\x*; laya ukukhululwa kukaJakobe\x + Hlab. 133.3.\x*.
\v 5 Ngawe sizadudula izitha zethu\x + Dute. 33.17.\x*; ngebizo lakho sizabanyathelela phansi abasivukelayo\x + Hlab. 60.12.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba kangithembeli\x + Hlab. 33.16. 1 Sam. 17.47.\x* kulo idandili lami\x + Josh. 24.12.\x*, lenkemba yami kayiyikungisindisa.
\v 7 Kodwa usisindisile ezitheni zethu, wayangisa abasizondayo\x + Hlab. 35.4. 40.14.\x*.
\v 8 KuNkulunkulu siyazincoma usuku lonke; lebizo lakho sizalidumisa kuze kube nininini. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 34.2.\x*.
