\v 9 Kodwa ulahlile wasiyangisa\x + 44.23. Hlab. 43.2. 60.1,10. 74.1. 77.7. 88.14. 89.38. 108.11. Lilo 2.7. 1 Lan. 28.9. Hlab. 89.38-45.\x*, njalo kawuphumi lamabutho ethu\x + Hlab. 60.10. 108.11.\x*.
\v 10 Usenze ukuthi sibuyele emuva sisuka esitheni; labasizondayo baziphangela\x + Hlab. 56.9. Levi 26.17.\x*.
\v 11 Usinikele njengezimvu zokudliwa\x + 44.22. Isa. 41.2.\x*, wasichithachitha phakathi kwezizwe\x + Hlab. 106.27. 139.3. Levi 26.33.\x*.
\v 12 Uthengisile abantu bakho ngokungelanotho\x + Dute. 32.30.\x*, awuzuzanga lutho ngentengo yabo\x + Isa. 52.3. Jer. 15.13.\x*.
\v 13 Usenze\x + Hlab. 39.8.\x* saba lihlazo kwabakhelene lathi\x + Neh. 2.17.\x*\x + Hlab. 79.4. 89.41. Hlab. 80.6.\x*, inhlekisa\x + Hlab. 79.4. 89.41. Hlab. 80.6.\x* lendumazo kwabasiphahlileyo\x + Hlab. 79.4. 89.41. Hlab. 80.6.\x*\x + Jer. 20.8.\x*.
\v 14 Usenze saba yisiga phakathi kwezizwe\x + Jer. 24.9. Jobe 17.6.\x*, ukunikinwa kwekhanda phakathi kwabantu\x + 2 Kho. 19.21.\x*.
\v 15 Usuku lonke ukudunyazwa kwami kuphambi kwami, lehlazo lobuso bami lingigubuzele\x + 2 Lan. 32.21.\x*,
