\v 24 Ufihlelani ubuso bakho, ukhohlwe ukuhlupheka kwethu locindezelo lwethu\x + Jobe 13.24.\x*?
\v 25 Ngoba umphefumulo wethu ukhothamele othulini, isisu sethu sinamathela emhlabathini\x + Hlab. 119.25.\x*.
\v 26 Sukumela usizo lwethu, usihlenge ngenxa yomusa wakho.